Version 0.2.1:
 * Improved API exceptions handling
 * New method in GoGridManager - get_server() which returns
   information about a single server (grid/server/get API call)
 * Support 'state' property of the image
 * New tool: gg-image-delete for removing images
 * Make gg-image-list tool not show images with state Trash unless
   '-a' flag was specified

Version 0.2.0:
 * Support API v 1.2, including MyGSI
 * Use XML instead of CSV which seems to be more reliable and error-prone
 * Support for multiple config profiles

Version 0.1.2:
 * Add support for server deletion by regexp

Version 0.1.1:
 * Fisrt public release
